{"tid":609603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國台灣交換生聲言發動校園槍擊被捕！！","createTime":"2018-03-29T07:21:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T23:34:50.000Z","uid":119778,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"25d42147c12fe437f016827ab625a89543f2d4e1","tid":609603,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T07:21:50.000Z","msg":"美國警方拘捕一名18歲台灣交換生，指他計劃在就讀的高中發動槍擊，被控製造恐怖威脅罪，目前收押於賓夕法尼亞州監獄，等候下月提堂。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，被告在學校課堂用的平板電腦，搜尋如何購買AK-47及AR-15半自動步槍，並向同學透露計劃在五月一日進行槍擊。他亦曾帶一枚大口徑子彈到學校。警方其後搜查他的住所，發現防彈背心、加裝瞄準器的強力十字弓，以及可用於AK-47及AR-15的槍架。被告的代表律師指，被告只是向同學開玩笑，並沒有計劃發動校園槍擊，又指警方搜獲的物件，是參加學校萬聖節服裝比賽的道具。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20180329_20180329-085710.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2FNewsBoss%2Fresize%2F20180329_20180329-085710.jpg&h=f2b37558&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"44e65882866f72e6e8274f80f58a219695d32090","tid":609603,"uid":11962,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T07:25:39.000Z","msg":"風頭火勢仲講呢啲，真係抵九死"},{"pid":"77a20b8d907c83214fa165f9792c15c5a680c9dc","tid":609603,"uid":56401,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T07:28:19.000Z","msg":"返中國啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d444040f534ddcf1bdfc1c18e31e19a4744dfa01","tid":609603,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T07:31:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180329/1324302/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180329%2F1324302%2F&d=WtV8rLE4pArhkj3eEZDXmTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=93c071ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180329%2F1324302%2F&h=f9bcd343\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180329/132430